= aptinstaller

* http://github.com/ngauthier/aptinstaller/tree/master

== DESCRIPTION:
This gem installs packages through apt-get in a similar manner as geminstaller installs gems.

== Usage:
aptinstaller [/full/path/to/rails/project/root]

